Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.94,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1139,137)\frz344.966}努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.94,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,605)\frz6.073}超
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.94,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(152,631)}努
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.94,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(185,647)}力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:24.07,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,408)}把握\N全局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:24.07,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz344.966\pos(1108,319)}努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:24.19,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz344.966\pos(1112,572)\blur3}努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:24.19,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(652,657)}把握\N全局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我 太一和肉包小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹着小奏和书桌小子 把状态调动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其应付对手的出赛顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如采取能让我们百分之百发挥实力的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不管对手是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都要赢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:54.07,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fade(245,0,255,0,900,4040,5010)\pos(490,285)}迢递天风起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是瑞泽高中的顺序表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛小子 睫毛小子!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说啦 你们打入决赛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千早也在最佳状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来都不知道 千早也会感到有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 千早也会?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为千早总是很强势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我选择了错误的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让她变得那么脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我居然连千早都不了解」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得接受这个事实对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我 是部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样 所以我才一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就算赌上全部青春 也不可能变得比新更强」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}回想起你们习惯的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}没问题 绝对能行的!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是另外一个你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那边发现了一个还是老样子的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩罗牌解答!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩罗浩罗浩罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方出战阵型是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说有很多变动是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 不用那么在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们又不是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来对付5号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿这儿这儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来对付3号的真岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦子 这是为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候 我和这家伙在同一个歌留多会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有输过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定会觉得我很棘手!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.51,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(173,56)\fade(205,0,205,0,147,4068,4670)}真…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:50.51,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(253,56)\fade(205,0,205,0,63,3108,3710)}真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:50.51,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(303,56)\fade(205,0,205,0,63,2948,3550)}的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.51,writings3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,56)\fade(205,0,205,0,63,2778,3380)}会
