Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其他人就随便决定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预选赛这玩意就赶紧轻松拿下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定要向静冈的富士崎高中报仇才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以全胜成绩拿下全国冠军!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸…诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中只有远方的话 当心脚下被绊倒哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啦是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个交上去吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你可能已经觉得腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今年我们也会带你去近江神宫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在宣布决赛的顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央学园 甘糟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中 西田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央学园 龙崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中 大江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央学园 木梨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中 真岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央学园 宅间同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中 驹野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北央学园 须藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞泽高中 绫濑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全猜中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩罗牌…真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对不起」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对不起」呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经说了「抱歉」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说「对不起」就不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请将牌摆好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面进入暗记时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这人怎么搞的啊
