Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.09,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1200,385)}我是千早。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.09,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1095,401)}新，生日那天的邮件谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:20.09,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fay0.13\c&HCCA28B&\an5\fs30\pos(1065,441)}没想到新会记得呢，吓我一跳。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.60,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&HC28B6F&\pos(294,85)}东京都预赛的联系来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.60,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1177,439)}成功了——!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.60,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1110,484)}凑齐了五个队员，可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.60,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HBE8C6B&\fs30\pos(1096,530)}参加大会了! 今天把材料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(334,90)}瑞泽高中的第一次胜利!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1191,482)}赢啦——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1148,528)}太一和肉包小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.48,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(1194,571)}状态都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.35,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(252,91)}分组赛胜出咯!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.35,writings5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(288,583)}3胜0败从B组出线了!
